{"tid":666322,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人鍾意NakamuraEmi","createTime":"2018-05-15T18:32:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T03:45:56.000Z","uid":12421,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4a7d85721ffe4f74259ed90bfc6035a39763a479","tid":666322,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T18:32:21.000Z","msg":"我喺由佢幫暗黑推銷員定唔知叫笑臉推銷員唱ed嗰陣開始留意佢 因為覺得佢Rap得型得嚟 啲歌詞又幾有意思 好正面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢把聲真係好啱Rap<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 磁性得嚟帶點性感<br />\n<br />\n咁講歌手當然唔少得歌啦 我最鍾意佢嘅嗰兩首歌都係喺同一隻碟到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一首係YAMABIKO<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=BGVUiMskx_U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBGVUiMskx_U&d=pPGJYqMZWzvH3DasdLYL2YzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=2b3b25d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=BGVUiMskx_U</a><br />\n<br />\n而首歌個感覺好熱血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每次做運動/周圍行去發掘新事物嗰陣都會好想聽 加上佢嗰啲振奮人心嘅歌詞 真係令人按捺不住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二首係女子達<br />\n<br />\n而首喺youtube搵唔到佢唱嘅version<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只係得人哋唱嘅version 真係有興趣嘅巴打可以去iTunes/其他音樂apps到試下聽<br />\n<br />\n首歌嘅節奏感配合佢想講嘅內容 真係倍添威力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢除咗rap之後 唱其實都好掂 譬如話 七夕、大人の言うことを聞け等等<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=Tohr3D3a_1Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTohr3D3a_1Y&d=pPGJYqMZWzvH3DasdLYL2YzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=550940dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=Tohr3D3a_1Y</a><br />\n<br />\n佢utube唔見有好多歌 所以喺到都冇乜歌好擺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但佢擺得上utube嘅歌都真係幾好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我見好多人都幾鍾意今季megalo box首ed 好開心咁多人鍾意佢嘅歌 所以一嚟想再分享下佢啲歌 二嚟想睇下有冇同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bcf625c471065b9c6ad585275637969118baaa9","tid":666322,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T20:16:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"968a1509754f975bb0caeeaacd6b51e3f148e3ef","tid":666322,"uid":23023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T01:29:10.000Z","msg":"近排係咁聽佢首yamabiko同megalo box 既ed<br />\n其實don&rsquo;t都唔錯<br />\n真心把聲好獨特同好好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c9a64e5da34f8dced95cfe306573e69c061089","tid":666322,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T03:45:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}